description: Associate a protect configuration with a configuration set. This replaces the configuration sets current protect configuration. A configuration set can only be associated with one protect configuration at a time. A protect configuration can be associated with multiple configuration sets.

parameters.name: ProtectConfigurationId
parameters.description: The unique identifier for the protect configuration.

nested_items.name: ConfigurationSetArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the configuration set.

nested_items.name: ProtectConfigurationArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the protect configuration.

nested_items.name: ProtectConfigurationId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier for the protect configuration.
